{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 17 depicts a general view of the malignant polyps entirely identified using UNet semantic segmentation.",
    "The Dice coefficient, which is the same as the IoU, is also used as a metric of segmentation precision.",
    "It is calculated Given an IoU of 0.93, the Dice coefficient can be determined as follows.",
    "Dice = 2 x 0.93/1 + 0.93=0.962.",
    "The Dice coefficient's high value further indicates that this method is effective in the accurate segmentation of polyps from colonoscopy images."
  ]
}